data.description: Welcome to Riverhills!  This neighborhood is located minutes from the towns of Shallotte and Holden Beach.  Enjoy your days at the community pool or pier overlooking the Shallotte River.   Upon entering this 3 bedroom and 2 bath home you will notice the sliding glass doors on either side of the fireplace that open to the back deck and shaded backyard.  The backyard is full of numerous plants as well as Japanese Maple, Live Oak, and Fig trees.  The kitchen is equipped with a range, dishwasher, microwave, and refrigerator. A beautiful lighted hanging pot rack is also included.   Make your appointment today to see this home.
